Qashqai e-Power 2WD N-Connecta: 40.600 euro
Qashqai e-Power 2WD N-Design: 43.100 euro
Qashqai e-Power 2WD Tekna: 43.100 euro
Qashqai e-Power 2WD Tekna+: 47.100 euro

